    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing a rare find for even the most discerning buyer. Every aspect of the car has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless exterior paint and pristine interior to the mechanical components that operate as they did the day it left the showroom. It has been garage-kept, regularly maintained with no expense spared, and shows no signs of wear or age. This is a collector-grade example that offers a like-new driving experience and remains in showroom-quality state throughout.",
